com.tangosol.util.function

Interface Remote.DoubleBinaryOperator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DoubleBinaryOperator, Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    Remote
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public static interface Remote.DoubleBinaryOperator
extends DoubleBinaryOperator, Serializable
    Represents an operation upon two double-valued operands and producing a double-valued result. This is the primitive type specialization of BinaryOperator for double.

    This is a functional interface whose functional method is DoubleBinaryOperator.applyAsDouble(double, double).

    See Also:
    BinaryOperator, Remote.DoubleUnaryOperator

    • Method Summary

      • Methods inherited from interface java.util.function.DoubleBinaryOperator

        applyAsDouble
